llm_outputs.rationale: The table on page 66 provides minimum dimensional requirements for different zoning districts. For the B-1 (Commercial District), there are three different minimum lot sizes depending on the availability of public water and sewer services.
llm_outputs.answer: 20,000 sq ft (no public water or sewer); 15,000 sq ft (public water or sewer); 10,000 sq ft (public water and sewer)
